{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state chec